---
/**
 * ClinicStory — enhanced · real image · pull-quote · stat accent bars
 */
---

<section class="story section" aria-labelledby="story-heading">
  <div class="story-wrap">

    <!-- Text side -->
    <div class="story-text">
      <span class="story-eye">Our Story</span>
      <h2 id="story-heading" class="story-h2">
        Serving Queens<br/>Since 1987
      </h2>
      <p class="story-lead">
        Founded in 1987, Smile Savers Dental was built on a simple philosophy — every patient in Woodside deserves exceptional, compassionate dental care delivered in a welcoming, family-oriented environment.
      </p>
      <div class="story-body">
        <p>
          For over three decades, our practice has been a trusted cornerstone of the Queens community. What began as a neighborhood dental office has grown into a modern, state-of-the-art facility serving multiple generations of local families.
        </p>
        <p>
          Today, Smile Savers is powered by a collaborative team of experienced dentists. By combining advanced digital dental technology—such as CEREC same-day crowns and 3D imaging—with a gentle, personalized touch, we ensure that your care is as comfortable as it is precise.
        </p>
        <p>
          While our techniques and team have evolved over the years, our core vision remains the same: putting your comfort first and helping you make informed, confident decisions about your oral health.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Pull quote -->
      <blockquote class="story-quote">
        <p>"Our goal is to combine state-of-the-art dentistry with the warmth, trust, and personal attention of a neighborhood family practice."</p>
        <cite>— The Smile Savers Team</cite>
      </blockquote>

      <!-- Stats -->
      <div class="story-stats">
        <div class="ss">
          <span class="ss-num">1987</span>
          <span class="ss-lbl">Founded</span>
        </div>
        <div class="ss">
          <span class="ss-num">35+</span>
          <span class="ss-lbl">Years Serving Queens</span>
        </div>
        <div class="ss">
          <span class="ss-num">10,000+</span>
          <span class="ss-lbl">Happy Patients</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Image side -->
    <div class="story-visual">
      <div class="story-img-wrap">
        <img
          src="/images/clinic-interior.jpg"
          alt="Smile Savers dental clinic — modern, welcoming practice in Woodside, Queens"
          width="800" height="900"
          loading="lazy"
          class="story-img"
        />
        <div class="story-img-badge">
          <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10z"/></svg>
          <div>
            <span class="sib-top">Modern Dentistry</span>
            <span class="sib-sub">State-of-the-Art Care</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>

<style>
.story { background: var(--color-surface-elevated) }
.story-wrap {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 1fr;
  gap: clamp(2.5rem,5vw,5rem);
  max-width: var(--container-xl);
  margin-inline: auto;
  padding-inline: clamp(.75rem,3vw,var(--spacing-element));
  align-items: center;
}
@media(min-width:900px){ .story-wrap { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr } }

/* Text */
.story-eye {
  display: inline-block;
  font-size: .7rem; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: .1em; text-transform: uppercase;
  color: var(--color-secondary-dark);
  background: rgba(61,186,167,.1);
  border-radius: 9999px; padding: .25rem .875rem;
  margin-bottom: .875rem;
}
.story-h2 {
  font-size: clamp(1.9rem,3.5vw,2.75rem);
  font-family: var(--font-family-heading);
  font-weight: 700; color: var(--color-primary);
  letter-spacing: -.025em; line-height: 1.1;
  margin: 0 0 1.25rem;
}
.story-lead {
  font-size: var(--font-size-lg); color: var(--color-text);
  font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.6;
  margin: 0 0 1.5rem;
}
.story-body { color: var(--color-text-muted); line-height: 1.8; margin-bottom: 1.75rem }
.story-body p { margin: 0 0 1rem }
.story-body p:last-child { margin-bottom: 0 }
.story-body strong { color: var(--color-primary); font-weight: 600 }

/* Pull quote */
.story-quote {
  border-left: 3px solid var(--color-secondary);
  padding-left: 1.25rem;
  margin: 0 0 2rem;
}
.story-quote p {
  font-size: clamp(1.05rem,1.8vw,1.2rem);
  font-style: italic; color: var(--color-text);
  line-height: 1.55; margin: 0 0 .5rem;
}
.story-quote cite { font-size: .82rem; color: var(--color-text-muted); font-style: normal; font-weight: 600 }

/* Stats */
.story-stats { display: flex; gap: 1.5rem; flex-wrap: wrap }
.ss {
  display: flex; flex-direction: column;
  padding-left: 1rem;
  border-left: 3px solid var(--color-accent);
}
.ss-num {
  font-size: clamp(1.4rem,2.5vw,1.75rem);
  font-family: var(--font-family-heading);
  font-weight: 800; color: var(--color-primary);
  letter-spacing: -.02em; line-height: 1;
}
.ss-lbl { font-size: .72rem; color: var(--color-text-muted); font-weight: 500; margin-top: .2rem }

/* Image */
.story-visual { position: relative }
.story-img-wrap {
  position: relative;
  border-radius: 1.5rem;
  overflow: hidden;
  box-shadow: 0 24px 60px rgba(16,43,63,.15);
  aspect-ratio: 4/5;
}
.story-img {
  width: 100%; height: 100%;
  object-fit: cover; object-position: center 20%;
  display: block;
}
.story-img-badge {
  position: absolute; bottom: 1.25rem; left: 1.25rem;
  display: flex; align-items: center; gap: .75rem;
  background: rgba(16,43,63,.9);
  backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
  color: #fff;
  padding: .875rem 1.25rem;
  border-radius: .875rem;
  border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.15);
}
.story-img-badge svg { color: var(--color-secondary); flex-shrink: 0; width: 22px; height: 22px }
.sib-top { display: block; font-size: .75rem; font-weight: 700; color: var(--color-secondary); letter-spacing: .03em }
.sib-sub { display: block; font-size: .68rem; color: rgba(255,255,255,.6) }
</style>
